{"tid":2369076,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"蘋人誌：專訪李婉華 緊貼香港新聞 因此堅守黃線 不像一般香港移民久居變藍","createTime":"2021-01-16T18:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T04:42:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":83,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"765cff59e693a04ea07560d7f7c0aff3d1c381d5","tid":2369076,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T18:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Zu-zosXwrf96iuvtR26fpe2uD0Y=/802x450/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U376BNP37JGHDIXA7PJMM7QVOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZu-zosXwrf96iuvtR26fpe2uD0Y%3D%2F802x450%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU376BNP37JGHDIXA7PJMM7QVOY.jpg&h=63a9f887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zzeJhXcdIWMA2a8EgXKZLvr_1Rg=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PWVTKOSRLRFAXACBHPSLFDU6WQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzzeJhXcdIWMA2a8EgXKZLvr_1Rg%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPWVTKOSRLRFAXACBHPSLFDU6WQ.jpg&h=974cdedf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IOQyDMuqbPXhg_ZxGI3BAQ6Lkqc=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ESXXF247UZCS5PWZYBPKQ7DR7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIOQyDMuqbPXhg_ZxGI3BAQ6Lkqc%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FESXXF247UZCS5PWZYBPKQ7DR7A.jpg&h=e643eb70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_zhC1YXzxatrq5bocg1ZNtGwLjI=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LIB5YVIDXZF7HNRV6XFH3NV4GI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_zhC1YXzxatrq5bocg1ZNtGwLjI%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLIB5YVIDXZF7HNRV6XFH3NV4GI.jpg&h=d6591349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說當時李婉華年屆30中期，中期報告顯示她處於事業收成期，她解釋：「收入等各方面好穩定，但我好辛苦，你知做這行一點不容易，特別是我這些半紅不黑。」然後她認識了未來夫婿、金融人李守正，對方有意組織家庭，李小姐眼前一亮，「你知我們這行能夠組織家庭的男人不是很多，而且很少男人會說組織家庭，我覺得，咦，原來圈外有這些男人。」<br />\n<br />\n想不到她將自己演藝生涯定性為半紅不黑，更想不到其家庭觀念很重，「我自己很憧憬有個家庭，但我憧憬的家庭，一直以來在娛樂圈的對象未必能provide給我。我只不過想要一個很普通的家庭，老公很愛這個家，一起生活，一起raise小朋友，我又會煮飯，一般正常家庭就是這樣。在我的圈子，我認識的男人不是不好，但不是我要的類型。」<br />\n<br />\n賺錢買花戴？卑詩省花草甚多，她靠工作衝出變遷之間的迷失，也為節目緊貼香港新聞，因此堅守黃線，不像一般香港移民久居變藍，「幸好在電台做了15年，雖然他們這樣對我，我不開心，但我飲水思源。」這裏是說去年電台將其每周五天直播節目大減至一小時錄播，莫非是她播放《榮光》之故？「公司說是疫情關係，大家知道啦，等於有線炒幾十人，都說是疫情關係。」未幾也丟了YouTube頻道《住加女人》，她不容一生被毀滅，另起爐灶《移加李婉華》。<br />\n<br />\n「香港人自製階級，這裏沒有，人人平等。」<br />\n<br />\n話雖住家傭工，一天規定工作八小時，一晚李婉華洗澡，女兒在外哭得淒厲，好媽媽怕她窒息，趕出來察看，反而姐姐死守香閨，原來八小時已過，「你不能告她，她沒有錯。」Madam但見碟子洗完仍與番茄皮藕斷絲連，溫提姐姐一句，這下好了，假日輪到madam做家務，忽然姐姐拿碟起義，訓示：「你個碟都有條米粉啦！」<br />\n<br />\n如此說來她要洗四個廁所？「我洗四個廁所，不是說笑，當然有part time間中幫我。自己廁所自己洗，洗廁所有何難度？」洗廁所不難，難在明星落手操刀，她即說：「你不要當我是明星，來到這裏沒這回事，這裏沒有階級。香港人自製階級，這裏沒有，人人平等，來到這裏不用自大也不用自卑。你ego大，所以感覺人家看你不起，其實沒有，所以男人有個問題，ego太大。」<br />\n<br />\n她勸移民人士放下包袱，別再比較香港與他方，「如果你的過去給你少少benefit你就利用，例如學識、技能，用不到便算，從頭來過。」忘掉過往四圈，執位再打過，「你來到這邊沒有包袱，沒有人識你，即使識你又如何，沒有人看不起人，你做藍領隨時賺多過白領，只有香港變態分階級。」一切風霜都捱過，她在溫哥華安身立命，「移民並非可怕，但你一定要堅強，將你的自尊心降低，能屈能伸，別怕辛苦，會有好結果，這裏定有一片天。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/E4Y7TYB26VFKNEOPJ3XVAIIPK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FE4Y7TYB26VFKNEOPJ3XVAIIPK4%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHCfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=d20000ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FE4Y7TYB26VFKNEOPJ3XVAIIPK4%2F&h=af04edd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/E4Y7TYB26VFKNEOPJ3XVAIIPK4/</a>"},{"pid":"04756a0641565829f6839f438b401a7e6da735ed","tid":2369076,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T18:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c83b0f6c384f4615b889ed000f9c1c5cc25904f","tid":2369076,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T19:03:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed04ba8257e13d45098babea51b6696621d01f25","tid":2369076,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T19:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc29396472d186c1be797cb674ef4b58de2657c4","tid":2369076,"uid":263534,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T19:11:25.000Z","msg":"仲keep到咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bea67fed18ae8b64055a45fa019255d6645e3d5","tid":2369076,"uid":8113,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTim